quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  64,10,"Wallatheena kafaroo wakaththaboobi-ayatina ola-ika as-habuannari khalideena feeha wabi/sa almaseer"
  64,11,"Ma asaba min museebatinilla bi-ithni Allahi waman yu/min billahiyahdi qalbahu wallahu bikulli shay-in AAaleem"
  64,12,"WaateeAAoo Allaha waateeAAooarrasoola fa-in tawallaytum fa-innama AAalarasoolina albalaghu almubeen"
  64,13,"Allahu la ilaha illahuwa waAAala Allahi falyatawakkali almu/minoon"
  64,14,"Ya ayyuha allatheena amanooinna min azwajikum waawladikum AAaduwwan lakum fahtharoohumwa-in taAAfoo watasfahoo wataghfiroo fa-inna Allahaghafoorun raheem"
  64,15,"Innama amwalukum waawladukumfitnatun wallahu AAindahu ajrun AAatheem"
  64,16,"Fattaqoo Allaha maistataAAtum wasmaAAoo waateeAAoo waanfiqookhayran li-anfusikum waman yooqa shuhha nafsihi faola-ikahumu almuflihoon"
  64,17,"In tuqridoo Allaha qardanhasanan yudaAAifhu lakum wayaghfir lakum wallahushakoorun haleem"
  64,18,"AAalimu alghaybi washshahadatialAAazeezu alhakeem"
